Actions.Text: REFERRED TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS
COMMITTEE DISCHARGED AND COMMITTED TO RULES

Title: Changes the official name of the Staten Island Expressway to the POW-MIA Memorial Highway
Summary: Changes the official name of the Staten Island Expressway to the "POW-MIA Memorial Highway".
LawCode: Amd §§340-a, 343-a & 349-f, Hway L; amd §11-243, NYC Ad Cd
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law and the administrative code of the city of New York, in relation to renaming the Staten Island Expressway the "POW-MIA Memorial Highway"
